This paper belongs to the sub-category of AI called Neural Networks. 

Explanation: The title and abstract of the paper clearly indicate that the focus is on gene regulation and biological development in neural networks. The paper explores an exploratory model that uses neural networks to understand how gene regulation affects biological development. While other sub-categories of AI may also be relevant to this topic, such as genetic algorithms or probabilistic methods, the primary focus of the paper is on neural networks.
